001package com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.response.historyLog;
002
003import com.google.common.base.Preconditions;
004import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.annotations.HistoryLogProps;
005import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.helpers.Bytes;
006
007@HistoryLogProps(
008    opCode = 74,
009    displayName = "Global Settings Change",
010    usedByTidepool = true
011)
012public class ParamChangeGlobalSettingsHistoryLog extends HistoryLog {
013    
014    private int modifiedData;
015    private int qbDataStatus;
016    private int qbActive;
017    private int qbDataEntryType;
018    private int qbIncrementUnits;
019    private int qbIncrementCarbs;
020    private int buttonVolume;
021    private int qbVolume;
022    private int bolusVolume;
023    private int reminderVolume;
024    private int alertVolume;
025    
026    public ParamChangeGlobalSettingsHistoryLog() {}
027    public ParamChangeGlobalSettingsHistoryLog(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, int modifiedData, int qbDataStatus, int qbActive, int qbDataEntryType, int qbIncrementUnits, int qbIncrementCarbs, int buttonVolume, int qbVolume, int bolusVolume, int reminderVolume, int alertVolume) {
028        super(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum);
029        this.cargo = buildCargo(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum, modifiedData, qbDataStatus, qbActive, qbDataEntryType, qbIncrementUnits, qbIncrementCarbs, buttonVolume, qbVolume, bolusVolume, reminderVolume, alertVolume);
030        this.modifiedData = modifiedData;
031        this.qbDataStatus = qbDataStatus;
032        this.qbActive = qbActive;
033        this.qbDataEntryType = qbDataEntryType;
034        this.qbIncrementUnits = qbIncrementUnits;
035        this.qbIncrementCarbs = qbIncrementCarbs;
036        this.buttonVolume = buttonVolume;
037        this.qbVolume = qbVolume;
038        this.bolusVolume = bolusVolume;
039        this.reminderVolume = reminderVolume;
040        this.alertVolume = alertVolume;
041        
042    }
043
044    public ParamChangeGlobalSettingsHistoryLog(int modifiedData, int qbDataStatus, int qbActive, int qbDataEntryType, int qbIncrementUnits, int qbIncrementCarbs, int buttonVolume, int qbVolume, int bolusVolume, int reminderVolume, int alertVolume) {
045        this(0, 0, modifiedData, qbDataStatus, qbActive, qbDataEntryType, qbIncrementUnits, qbIncrementCarbs, buttonVolume, qbVolume, bolusVolume, reminderVolume, alertVolume);
046    }
047
048    public int typeId() {
049        return 74;
050    }
051
052    /**
053     * <table border="1">
054     * <caption>Parsed fields for ParamChangeGlobalSettingsHistoryLog:</caption>
055     * <tr><td><code>modifiedData</code></td><td><code>raw[10]</code></td></tr>
056     * <tr><td><code>qbDataStatus</code></td><td><code>raw[11]</code></td></tr>
057     * <tr><td><code>qbActive</code></td><td><code>raw[12]</code></td></tr>
058     * <tr><td><code>qbDataEntryType</code></td><td><code>raw[13]</code></td></tr>
059     * <tr><td><code>qbIncrementUnits</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 14)</code></td></tr>
060     * <tr><td><code>qbIncrementCarbs</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 16)</code></td></tr>
061     * <tr><td><code>buttonVolume</code></td><td><code>raw[18]</code></td></tr>
062     * <tr><td><code>qbVolume</code></td><td><code>raw[19]</code></td></tr>
063     * <tr><td><code>bolusVolume</code></td><td><code>raw[20]</code></td></tr>
064     * <tr><td><code>reminderVolume</code></td><td><code>raw[21]</code></td></tr>
065     * <tr><td><code>alertVolume</code></td><td><code>raw[22]</code></td></tr>
066     * </table>
067     */
068    public void parse(byte[] raw) {
069        Preconditions.checkArgument(raw.length == 26);
070        this.cargo = raw;
071        parseBase(raw);
072        this.modifiedData = raw[10];
073        this.qbDataStatus = raw[11];
074        this.qbActive = raw[12];
075        this.qbDataEntryType = raw[13];
076        this.qbIncrementUnits = Bytes.readShort(raw, 14);
077        this.qbIncrementCarbs = Bytes.readShort(raw, 16);
078        this.buttonVolume = raw[18];
079        this.qbVolume = raw[19];
080        this.bolusVolume = raw[20];
081        this.reminderVolume = raw[21];
082        this.alertVolume = raw[22];
083        
084    }
085
086    public static byte[] buildCargo(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, int modifiedData, int qbDataStatus, int qbActive, int qbDataEntryType, int qbIncrementUnits, int qbIncrementCarbs, int buttonVolume, int qbVolume, int bolusVolume, int reminderVolume, int alertVolume) {
087        return HistoryLog.fillCargo(Bytes.combine(
088            new byte[]{74, 0},
089            Bytes.toUint32(pumpTimeSec),
090            Bytes.toUint32(sequenceNum),
091            new byte[]{ (byte) modifiedData }, 
092            new byte[]{ (byte) qbDataStatus }, 
093            new byte[]{ (byte) qbActive }, 
094            new byte[]{ (byte) qbDataEntryType }, 
095            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(qbIncrementUnits), 
096            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(qbIncrementCarbs), 
097            new byte[]{ (byte) buttonVolume }, 
098            new byte[]{ (byte) qbVolume }, 
099            new byte[]{ (byte) bolusVolume }, 
100            new byte[]{ (byte) reminderVolume }, 
101            new byte[]{ (byte) alertVolume }));
102    }
